<h1>Help</h1><br>
<h4>
<b>How to create a pdf file from a word document (curriculaem vitae):<br></b>
<i>
-Open your cv with a word program(e.g microsoft word application)<br>
-At the top, in the right hand corner, click on the file menu item<br>
-Choose the save as option from that list<br>
-When a dialog box opens up, choose a folder to save the file in<br>
-Click on the drop down menu to change the save format from word document(default) to PDF(portable document format)<br>
-that's it, hope you found this helpful.<br>
</i>
<h4>
